## Setup and Usage

### Step 1: Clone the repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/Alli15Powell/FinanceFlow-USA.git
cd FinanceFlow-USA


Step 2: Create and activate a virtual environment (recommended)

Windows

python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate


Mac/Linux

python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate

Step 3: Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

Step 4: Initialize the database
python core/db.py
python core/seed_db.py

Step 5: Run the application
python main.py

Reset Instructions

If your charts show no data or you encounter the error
pandas.errors.DatabaseError: file is not a database,
you can reset and rebuild the database using the following commands:

del data\financeflow.db          # Windows
# or
rm data/financeflow.db           # Mac/Linux

python core/db.py                # Recreate the database
python core/seed_db.py           # Reseed with example data


Then relaunch the app:

python main.py

